Package graph

Interface WeightedGraph<V>

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractUndirectedWeightedGraph, DenseUndirectedWeightedGraph, SpanningTree
public interface WeightedGraph<V>
Root interface of graph. A weighted graph is a collection of vertices and edges, where there is a weight associated with each edge.
